William QUICK, Plaintiff-Cross-Movant,
v.
Glenn KRAMER, Defendant. M-875/876 September Term 2017
080058 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 15, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for leave to appeal as within time (M-875) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal (M-876) is denied.
